snippet.title: Goodgame Empire's 5th Anniversary!
snippet.description:
We've made it this far thanks to each and every one of you! 

THANK YOU for standing by us and fighting side by side during these past 5 years! HAPPY BIRTHDAY brave warriors!

www.facebook.com/GoodgameEmpire

Five Armies by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution licence (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Source: http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/index.html?isrc=USUAN1100875
Artist: http://incompetech.com/

Danse Macabre - Busy Strings by Kevin MacLeod is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution licence (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Source: http://incompetech.com/music/royalty-free/index.html?isrc=USUAN1100556
Artist: http://incompetech.com/

Build up your castle, ally with friends and fight your enemies to become the king of a mighty empire in this fantastic MMO-strategy game. Play Goodgame Empire now for free in your browser or install the Empire: Four Kingdoms App on your iPad, iPhone or Android device. 

http://empire.goodgamestudios.com/

★ MMO of the Year 2013 „Best Strategy Browser MMO" für Goodgame Empire
★ European Games Award 2012 und 2014: „Best European Browser Game" für Goodgame Empire
★ BÄM! Award 2012: Kategorie „Online- oder Social-Game" für Goodgame Empire
